Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Minimum duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases involving 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in variants leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in variants ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to the next occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
